@Catalog.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Get all products
GET {{Catalog.API_HostAddress}}/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get product by ID (replace with actual ID after creating a product)
GET {{Catalog.API_HostAddress}}/products/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new product
POST {{Catalog.API_HostAddress}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "categories": ["Electronics", "Smartphones"],
  "description": "Latest iPhone with A17 Pro chip",
  "imageFile": "iphone15pro.jpg",
  "price": 999.99
}

###

### Update a product (replace ID with actual product ID)
PUT {{Catalog.API_HostAddress}}/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "name": "iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "categories": ["Electronics", "Smartphones"],
  "description": "Updated description for iPhone 15 Pro Max",
  "price": 1199.99,
  "imageUrl": "iphone15promax.jpg"
}

###

### Delete a product (replace with actual product ID)
DELETE {{Catalog.API_HostAddress}}/products/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

